        "title": "Does Docker alpine image support openjdk19",
        "body": "<p>Does Docker alpine image support openjdk19. If yes how do we install openjdk19 using Docker alpine image 3.16.2. I am able to install openjdk11 but not openjdk19.<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 74467215,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "dockerfile"
        ],
